These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, rat, chinchilla, hedgehog
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, pink, light-blue, azure, chestnut
1. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes azure is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the turtle is between the person who likes azure and the person who likes light-blue##2
6. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Pet          | cat | turtle | hedgehog | chinchilla | rat |
| Color   | light-blue  | chestnut      | azure   | blue     | pink    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, fuchsia, lavender, orange
5 different games are played: whist, go, scrabble, snooker, backgammon
1. the person who likes blood-red is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
5. the person playing whist is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person playing snooker##2
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Color   | fuchsia     | lavender       | orange    | blood-red | aquamarine   |
| Game      | go | whist | snooker | backgammon      | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
City: rome, new-york, nizza, hamburg, marseilles
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, taxi, motorbike, ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
6. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
7. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| City         | rome | nizza | new-york | hamburg    | marseilles |
| Transport   | ship     | car        | motorbike      | taxi | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, american, polish, brazilian, canadian
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, lavender, coral, grey, mauve
1. the polish is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
4. the canadian is the person who likes lavender##1
5. the polish is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the american is between the person who likes coral and the canadian##2
7. the person who likes mauve is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Nationality         | thai      | brazilian | polish | american   | canadian  |
| Color   | grey | mauve    | coral        | pink | lavender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, pink, white, black, aquamarine
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, blend, game, havana, prince
1. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes pink is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person who likes black is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
5. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes grey is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
7. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes white is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Color      | aquamarine      | pink | grey   | black  | white  |
| Cigar   | game | havana | oliveros | blend | prince |

