.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, musical, martial-arts, action
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, soccer, baseball, climbing
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | fantasy                | martial-arts  | musical  | action            |
| Sport        | water-polo | climbing | ice-hockey | soccer | baseball |

