.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
House: cape-cod, craftsman, cottage, palace, gothic-revival
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, sports, mystery, epic, drama
1. the palace house is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
3. the craftsman house is in the middle##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is in an odd position##4
6. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
9. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| House   | gothic-revival       | cottage   | craftsman    | palace    | cape-cod |
| Movie-Genre        | mystery | documentary | sports | drama | epic     |

