.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
House: art-deco, cottage, ranch-style, modern, craftsman
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, surfing, basketball, sailing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is basketball is the craftsman house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the modern house is in an even position##4
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is badminton##2
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| House      | ranch-style  | art-deco       | cottage      | modern  | craftsman   |
| Sport   | badminton | water-polo | sailing | surfing | basketball |

