.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, musician, teacher, dressmaker, designer
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, aconite, daffodil, sunflower
1. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
2. the dressmaker is the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the dressmaker##1
4. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
5. the musician is the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the teacher is between the musician and the scientist##2
7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the teacher##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Job   | designer | musician | teacher     | scientist | dressmaker |
| Flower           | marigold | begonia     | aconite | sunflower    | daffodil      |

