.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-10::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: traveling, chess, skydiving, fishing, woodworking
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, asparagus, pumpkin, watermelon, pomegranate
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating asparagus is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person eating watermelon is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Hobby     | woodworking | skydiving | fishing | traveling | chess |
| Food   | pumpkin | pomegranate | watermelon    | asparagus    | cranberry  |

