.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
5 different games are played: bridge, domino, whist, mah-jongg, poker
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, bluemaster, dannemann, davidoff, ritmeester
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
3. the person playing bridge is between the dannemann-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing whist##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
7. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Game    | domino    | poker  | bridge      | mah-jongg     | whist |
| Cigar   | fonseca | bluemaster | davidoff | dannemann | ritmeester |

