.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
House: cape-cod, palace, futuristic, townhouse, victorian
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, dressmaker, engineer, librarian, mechanic
1. the dressmaker is on the left of the engineer##1
2. the mechanic is the cape-cod house##1
3. the mechanic is in the middle##1
4. the palace house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
5. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the scientist is between the mechanic and the palace house##2
7. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
8. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
9. the mechanic is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| House        | townhouse | victorian | cape-cod  | futuristic | palace     |
| Job   | dressmaker  | engineer     | mechanic | scientist      | librarian |

