.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, june, july, august, september
City: prague, colone, paris, nizza, new-york
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's birthday is in july##2
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
8. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Birthday      | september       | july | june | august   | april   |
| City   | nizza | colone | new-york  | prague | paris |

