.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, water-polo, badminton, surfing, ice-hockey
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, action, time-travel, drama, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
7. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching action movies and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Sport    | ice-hockey   | surfing  | water-polo     | cycling | badminton |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | time-travel | western | drama | action      |

