.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, manager, pilot, software-developer, architect
There 5 different types of food: grapes, mango, watermelon, lime, apple
1. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
2. the teacher is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the teacher##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
6. the pilot is on the left or right of the manager##3
7. the person eating watermelon is in an odd position##4
8. the person eating lime is in the middle##1
9. the person eating mango is on the right of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Job   | manager  | pilot    | software-developer | teacher   | architect |
| Food   | apple | mango | lime    | grapes | watermelon |

