.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, marigold, dahlia, sunflower
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, juice, milk, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
9. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Flower   | bellflower | azalea | sunflower     | marigold | dahlia |
| Beverage     | milk       | sprite   | juice | hot-chocolate   | mirinda        |

