.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, futuristic, gothic-revival, modern
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking sprite is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the modern house##3
5. the modern house is between the farmhouse house and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the gothic-revival house and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
7. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| House         | gothic-revival | futuristic | cottage | modern | farmhouse     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate       | sprite | 7up |

