.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, ritmeester, prince, blend, tiparillo
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, analyst, photographer, chef, social-worker
1. the chef is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the photographer is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the analyst is between the social-worker and the chef##2
4. the photographer is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the blend-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the social-worker is the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | prince      | blend | tiparillo     | ritmeester      |
| Job     | social-worker | analyst | chef | teacher | photographer |

 